transcript: Hello, this is John Smith calling about a critical system outage. Our entire production environment has been down for the past 2 hours and we're losing money every minute. This is extremely urgent and needs immediate attention. Our customer ID is CUST-12345.

Hi, I'm calling to complain about my recent bill. I'm very frustrated because I was charged for services I didn't use. This is disappointing and I expect this to be resolved quickly. My account number is ACC-67890.
Hello, I just wanted to call and thank your support team for resolving my issue yesterday. The technician was very helpful and professional. Everything is working perfectly now. Great service!
Hi, I have a question about your new service offerings. Could you please send me some information about the pricing plans? I'm considering upgrading my current package.
